entry.title: TreeRex/cl-marc
entry.summary:
Library for reading Z39.2 / MARC files

Minimal support for reading MARC (ISO2709 / ANSI Z39.2) records.

Support in progress for MARC-21, UNIMARC, CMARC, CNMARC, and KORMARC.
